insert into helpdoc values(newid(), 'http://dev24.sandbox.projectinsight.net/projectinsight.webapp/api/help/model/customfield', '

CustomField

Defines an individual custom field for a built in object\, or custom item.

NameDescriptionType
ApplyNoWrapToFormLabelCell Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Input Label Apply No Wrap] - Applies no wrap to the cell holding the input label. boolean
Col Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Column] - The column the field will be displayed on the add/edit form. NOTE: The column field is ignored on certain forms where layout control is not permitted when the field is located on summary or details sections. integer
ColSpan Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Input Column Span] - The number of columns the field will span on the add/edit form. NOTE: The column span may not be honored on certain forms if the field is located in the summary or details location. integer
CssClass Gets or sets the string - [CSS Class] - The CSS class to be apply to the Custom Field. Input valid CSS classes from the system\, or custom interface CSS file. Note: Some input types do not use this property and setting the value will have no effect for controls which ignore this property.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
DataType Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Data Type] - The type of data the field will capture.

Remarks: Default Property

 integer
DefaultValue Gets or sets the string - [Default Value] - The default value for the control to prepopulate when not set for a new item.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
DisplayCol Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Column] - The column the field will be displayed on the display form. NOTE: The column setting is ignored on certain forms where layout control is not permitted when the field is located on summary or details sections. integer
DisplayColSpan Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Display Column Span] - The number of columns the field will span on the display form. NOTE: The column span may not be honored on certain forms if the field is located in the summary or details location. integer
DisplayColumnIsWrapText Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Table Column Wrap Text] - Whether or not the text wraps when displayed in a table. boolean
DisplayColumnName Gets or sets the string - [Table Column Name] - The name of the field which will be displayed on the table column heading when displayed in a table\, if specified. If not specified\, the field name is used. string
DisplayColumnWidth Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Table Column Width] - The default width in pixels of the field when displayed in a table.

Remarks: Default Property

 integer
DisplayCssClass Gets or sets the string - [Display CSS Class] - The CSS class or classes to be apply to the Display Control. Input valid CSS classes from the system\, or custom interface CSS file. Note: Some input types do not use this property and setting the value will have no effect for controls which ignore this property.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
DisplayFormatMask Gets or sets the string - [Format Mask] - The format mask to use for types that are converted to strings upon display of the information. The format string supplied will be used to format the value with the input format string. Use .NET format masks.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
DisplayHideColonOnFormLabel Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Display Label Hide Colon] - Hides the colon on the display label. boolean
DisplayLabelOrientation Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Display Label Orientation] - The display label orientation in relation to the display field on the display form. NOTE: When field is shown on the summary or detail location\, this setting may be ignored. integer
DisplayLocation Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Display Location] - The location of the field on the display form.

Remarks: Default Property

 integer
DisplayName Gets or sets the string - [Display Name] - The name of the field to when shown on a display form\, if specified. The field name is used if this value is not specified. string
DisplayName_Text Gets (read only) the string - [Display Name Text] - The name of the field to when shown on a display form\, if specified. The field name is used if this value is not specified. string
DisplayRow Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Display Row/Order] - The row the field will be displayed on the display form. integer
DisplayRowSpan Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Display Row Span] - The number of rows the field will span on the display form. NOTE: The row span may not be honored on certain forms if the field is located in the summary or details location. integer
EnableAsAvailableColumnInTable Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Enable as Column] - Enables the field as a selectable available column on reports.

Remarks: Default Property

 boolean
EnableGroupBy Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Enable Group By] - Enables group by functionality in the reports. boolean
EnableSumColumn Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Enable Sum Column] - Enables the column to be summed within the reports. (Only applies to numeric fields) boolean
FieldNumber Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Field #] - The fixed internal field number. Limited to 80 fields\, assigned automatically.

Remarks: Default Property

 integer
HelpText Gets or sets the string - [Help Text] - The help text which is displayed on the form in conjunction with the name.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
HelpTextAdditional Gets or sets the string - [Help Text Additional] - The additional help text to display with the form. string
HelpTextAdditionalColSpan Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Help Text Additional Col Span] - Number of columns for the Help Text column to span to prevent formatting issues. integer
HelpTextAdditionalInRightColumn Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Help Text Additional Display On Right] - Flag indicating whether or not the help text additional will be displayed on the right column instead of underneath the label boolean
HideColonOnFormLabel Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Input Label Hide Colon] - Hides the colon on the input label. boolean
Id Gets or sets the guid Id. guid
IdExternal Gets or sets the ProjectInsight.Models.Base.ApiModelBase.IdExternal object which allows the object to be saved with an associated external identification. Used primarily for integrations. IdExternal
InputControlType Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Input Control] - The type of input control the field will use.

Remarks: Default Property

 integer
InputCssClass Gets or sets the string - [Input CSS Class] - The CSS class or classes to be apply to the Input Control. Input valid CSS classes from the system\, or custom interface CSS file. Note: Some input types do not use this property and setting the value will have no effect for controls which ignore this property.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
InputLabelOrientation Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Input Label Orientation] - The input label orientation in relation to the input field on the add/edit form. NOTE: When field is shown on the summary or detail location\, this setting may be ignored. integer
InputLocation Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Input Location] - The location of the field on the add/edit form.

Remarks: Default Property

 integer
IsActive Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Active] - Determines whether or not the field is currently active. If not active the field does not display.

Remarks: Default Property

 boolean
IsDefaultDisplayColumn Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Default Column] - Whether or not the field is included as a default column when it"s displayed.

Remarks: Default Property

 boolean
IsFinancialData Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Financial Data] - Indicates that the value of the custom field is financial and therefore follows financial data visibility rules.

Remarks: Default Property

 boolean
IsReadOnly Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Read Only] - If the custom field is read only (the field will be updated programmatically) check the box.

Remarks: Default Property

 boolean
IsRequired Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Required] - The flag that determines whether the custom field is required when inputting using the forms.

Remarks: Default Property

 boolean
IsRequiredInline Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Required Inline] - The flag that determines whether the custom field is required when inputting inline. When true\, a field is automatically added as a Default Column for inline displays.

Remarks: Default Property

 boolean
IsShowAsReportFilter Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Show as Report Filter] - The flag that determines whether the field should show up as a choice on the reports filter.

Remarks: Default Property

 boolean
ListDisplaySeparator Gets or sets the string - [Display Separator] - The separator to use when multiple choices have been selected and the values are being displayed. string
ListItems Gets (read only) the Collection of T generic collection of ListItemValue objects

Remarks: Default Property

 Collection of ListItemValue
ListRepeatColumns Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Repeat Columns] - The number of columns to display the checkboxes or radio buttons in column format.

Remarks: Default Property

 integer
ListRepeatDirection Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Repeat Direction] - The repeat direction when displaying the choices for multi-choice controls. integer
ListRepeatLayout Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Repeat Layout] - The repeat layout to use in multi-choice controls. integer
Name Gets or sets the string - [Field Name] - The default name of the field displayed on the form.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
OnChange Gets or sets the string - [JS OnChange] - The JavaScript code to execute when the input onchange is fired. Input valid JavaScript on change code. Note: Some input types do not use this property and setting the value will have no effect for controls which ignore this property. For ComboBox controls you must create a function outside of this input and apply the name of that function to the combo box control. The function should be formatted like this function ComboBoxAfterChange(metafuseComboBox\, previousValue\, newValue) { };

Remarks: Default Property

 string
ReadOnlyProperty Gets or sets the string - [Read Only Property] - The property the read only value is retrieved from. string
ReadOnlyText Gets or sets the string - [Read Only Text] - The read only text that is associated with this field.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
Row Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Input Row/Order] - The row the field will be displayed on the add/edit form. integer
RowSpan Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Input Row Span] - The number of rows the field will span on the add/edit form. NOTE: The row span may not be honored on certain forms if the field is located in the summary or details location. integer
SerializeType Get or Set if the Type should be serialized boolean
StyleDisplayText Gets or sets the string - [Control Display CSS Style Text] - The CSS style text to apply to the display control. Input valid CSS style code. Note: Some input types do not use this property and setting the value will have no effect for controls which ignore this property.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
StyleText Gets or sets the string - [Control Input CSS Style Text] - The CSS style text to apply to the input control. Input valid CSS style code for text alteration. Note: Some input types do not use this property and setting the value will have no effect for controls which ignore this property.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
StyleTextCell Gets or sets the string - [Control Cell CSS Style Text] - The CSS style text that is applyed to the table cell which contains the input or display control. Input valid CSS style code for background alterations.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
StyleTextHeader Gets or sets the string - [Header CSS Style Text] - The CSS style text that is directly applyed to the Field Name and Display Name on a form. Input valid CSS style code.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
StyleTextHeaderCell Gets or sets the string - [Header Cell CSS Style Text] - The CSS style text that is applyed to the header table cell which contains the Field Name and Display Name on a form. Input valid CSS style code for background alterations.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
TextAlign Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Text Align] - The alignment of the text the left or the right of the user control.

Remarks: Default Property

 integer
TextBoxMaxLength Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Max Length] - The maximum number of characters that can be entered into the control. integer
TextBoxRows Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Rows] - The number of rows to display for the control.

Remarks: Default Property

 integer
Type Gets or sets the string object type for external reference\, rest calls. string
